race.comment: Just the four runners after scratchings with INSTA WORTHY (1) the standout after his solid return last start over 1210m at Lismore. Led for home that day but found the winner too strong in the closing stages. Added fitness and a shorter journey work in his favour. Will be very tough to catch. PRESTIGE PAK (3) returned in good order at Murwillumbah, overcoming a slow start to finish second over today's journey. Suited by the small field and with some added fitness will be tough to hold out. EGYPTIAN LASS (6) just missed at big odds here recently. Has been up for a while but if she bowls along in front again might be hard to catch. ZELENKA (8) gets a pass mark for her debut here last start. Should come on from that run.
